
Roland ran up to his friend. "Dude i signed us up for a job interview"
Phoenix eyed his friend warily, not sure he fully trusted him. "Whats the job"
"Can't you just trust me, I promise you'll like it"
Phoenix sighed, deciding to go along with his unruly friends plan "ok, c'mon lets go"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
"so what are your skills?"
'This guy has freaky eyebrows' Roland thought, looking at the guy who was interviewing them for the job. "I can beat up three guys at once" he said absentmindedly, before realizing that saying that wasnt likely to get you a job.
Phoenix facepalmed.